  stimulus_text = 'The invention of the printing press in the 15th century was a pivotal moment in the history of communication, ushering in a new era of widespread literacy and knowledge dissemination. Before the printing press, the vast majority of books were copied by hand, a process that was both time-consuming and costly. As a result, access to books was limited to a small, privileged few.',
