UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The debate over the use of artificial intelligence in the workplace is complex. Many people are concerned about the potential job losses that AI could cause; others worry about the ethical implications of using AI to make decisions that affect human lives. Despite these concerns, many business leaders believe that AI can help to improve efficiency and productivity. However, the transition to a workplace that relies heavily on AI will require careful planning and management.  According to many experts, it is likely that ______ the use of AI will become more widespread in the coming years.',
