The reason why many people prefer to eat at home rather than going to a restaurant is because of the cost.',
  stimulus_type = NULL,
  options = '[{"id":"A","text":"The reason why many people prefer to eat at home rather than going to a restaurant is because of the cost.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Choice A is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Compare this option against the grammar or logic rule tested by the stem before selecting a final answer."},{"id":"B","text":"Many people prefer to eat at home rather than going to a restaurant because of the cost.","is_correct":true,"explanation":"Choice B matches the question''s requirement and is consistent with the passage''s central claim or supporting detail. Compare this option against the grammar or logic rule tested by the stem before selecting a final answer."},{"id":"C","text":"Many people prefer to eat at home rather than going to a restaurant because the cost.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Choice C is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Compare this option against the grammar or logic rule tested by the stem before selecting a final answer."},{"id":"D","text":"The reason why many people prefer to eat at home rather than going to a restaurant is due to the cost.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"Choice D is incorrect because it either misreads the passage, overgeneralizes a limited detail, or focuses on information irrelevant to the question stem. Compare this option against the grammar or logic rule tested by the stem before selecting a final answer."}]'::jsonb,
